  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GoCoder
    GoCoder main class
    GoCoderBroadcastConfig
    This class represents the configuration needed by GoCoder SDK to connect to Wowza Streaming Cloud live stream
    Utilities
    Utilities
    WowzaAccount
    Register the Wowza GoCoder SDK API keys
    WowzaLiveStream
    Every instance of this class represents a Wowza Live Stream, that is indentified by its "name", "id" and "connection_code".
    WowzaLiveStreamParams
    Parameters used to create a WowzaLiveStream object, all properties (except "name") have a default value; see Ingest parameters for more info.
